HEADWORD: Millennialist
<hw>Mil*len"ni*al*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who believes that
Christ will reign personally on earth a thousand years; a Chiliast;
also, a believer in the universal prevalence of Christianity for a long
period.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

